From the main navigation select the page the form needs to be added to. 

Hover over the edge of a section the form is to be added after and select + ADD A SECTION 

Select a single column section and then clock on Form to add a form. 

Click on New Form 

Select the table the form data is to be saved to 

Select the form that has previously been created (see Creating a form) 

Give the form a name e.g. Create issue Form 

In Data select the function the form will carry out on the data e.g. Creates a new record / Is read only 

In the  On Submit option choose what happens after the form has been submitted 

Turn on CAPTCHA for anonymous users only. 

Enable attachments if required and choose appropriate options. Upload size limit is usually set to 5000 – 5Mb
